CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 3, 1971, pg. 20, reads: "Mrs. Grace Hatcher, working-wife and gourmet cook, loves soul food...chitterlings f'instance. But we reasoned everybody knows how to cook them, so we asked for a different recipe.  She came up with Cabbage Beef Rolls, which are Polish...or Spanish...of most any nationality."
TitMainTitle: Grace Hatcher wearing apron printed with wreath and candles, cooking in domestic kitchen
